cosine_to_target.description: Cosine similarity between projected query and target answer

mse_to_target.description: Mean Squared Error between projected query and target answer

target_rank.description: Position of correct answer when sorted by similarity (1-indexed)
target_rank.good_value: Lower is better (1 = correct answer is top result)

mrr.description: Mean Reciprocal Rank = average of 1/rank across all queries

recall_at_k.description: Fraction of queries where correct answer is in top k results
recall_at_k.good_value: Higher is better (1.0 = always in top k)
